description.text:
This is a remix of my customizable heart message (<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:247436/" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:247436/</a>) with the ability to add a loop for a necklace or a charm bracelet.  
I made it customizable so you can put in whatever message you want.  
In case you don't want to customize, I've uploaded stl's of &quot;I love you&quot; and &quot;My friend&quot;
